Asset Management Business

A part of the asset management division spun off from Mizuho Trust & Banking Co., Ltd. is integrated to Asset Management One Co., Ltd. on October 1st, 2016, established as an integrated company of the asset management functions of the following companies; DIAM Co., Ltd., Mizuho Asset Management Co., Ltd., and Shinko Asset Management Co., Ltd.
In order to provide the best asset management consulting services and the best solutions for the clients’ needs, we aim to improve the quality of our current asset management products and expand the product line–up, in close collaboration with Asset Management One Co., Ltd.


