It moves to the head on this page.


Investment Trusts

Activities and Services


Mizuho Securities responds to the customers' needs of growing diversity in customer asset management and assists them in asset formation through offering investment trusts and other products. To contribute to the creation of optimal portfolios for its customers, Mizuho Securities carefully selects asset management companies from around the world that are evaluated highly and have superior track records; the Company then packages these asset management services as investment trusts and delivers them to its customers.
Mizuho Securities offers investment trusts that invest in conventional financial instruments, such as equities and bonds, including those of issuers in Japan and overseas, as well as offers access to a broad range of asset classes, from hybrid securities, commodities, and loans to other investments. At Mizuho Securities, experienced staff analyze information on a daily basis to enable them to provide advice on investment products that meet customer needs. In addition, they supply timely information to customers regarding their investment portfolios.





