Corporate + Investment Banking







Our services dive deep into industry and client needs ranging from investment banking and advisory services to corporate, structured and project finance.
We’re guided by a mix of careful decision-making and creative approaches to the complex financial needs of our clients—primarily major corporations, public sector entities and financial institutions headquartered or operating within the Americas. 

Working in lock step with our specialists in M&A, debt and equity capital markets, futures, trade services, foreign exchange, and derivatives, we provide innovative strategic advisory and corporate finance solutions for our clients. Our customized solutions are supported by a global platform and made powerful by our network throughout the Americas. Our attentive teams develop and execute transactions to meet diverse needs including acquisition and divestitures, strategic capital raising, risk management, capital structure optimization, maintaining liquidity and securing financial flexibility.  





