Global Markets







For issuers and investors alike, our seasoned team of specialists is dedicated to helping our clients achieve the best possible results in all market conditions. We stay committed to our clients’ priorities and help provide stability for their future growth. 

As our capital markets expertise and execution capabilities have expanded over the years, we’ve listened to our clients’ needs to guide our offerings and strategic growth. Our solutions reflect the structure, diligence and attention-to-detail our clients expect and deserve. 
Despite the market turmoil of the past few years, we’ve strengthened our position as a partner to trust. Our solid balance sheet and experienced teams give clients the confidence and global access to navigate changing conditions.
With offices around the world, we seamlessly provide global coverage and execution services 24 hours a day. And, our access to all major US and international exchanges means no door is closed when working with us. 




Services


Equities

Fixed Income

Futures + Options

Derivatives

Foreign Exchange

US Private Placements









Comprehensive services in execution and origination
We provide our institutional and corporate clients with an array of services, including:
Origination capabilities across the product spectrum, including investment-grade and high-yield bonds, asset-backed securities and equity and equity-linked products
Sales and trading capabilities across equities and fixed income
Global futures with a full range of clearing and execution services 
Derivatives structuring and pricing 




